Package ptolemy.actor.lib.fmi Description

Functional Mock-up Interface (FMI) actors. The Functional Mock-up Interface (FMI) is an interface that is instantiated by a Functional Mock-up Unit (FMU) to provide co-simulation using different modeling tools.

Resources

  • http://functional-mockup-interface.org/
  • http://functional-mockup-interface.org/specifications/FMI_for_CoSimulation_v1.0.zip - FMI for Co-simulation
  • http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Functional_Mock-up_Interface

Since:
Ptolemy II 8.1
